However you should note that your solution is a lot more complicated than it needs to be, and the division that&#39;s causing the issue is completely redundant. 

The logic can be DRY&#39;d up and made much more extensible by removing the unique `id` attributes (which removes the need for the loop/array and the modulo operator) and also by using common classes on all your elements. Try this:

